{"tid":2067152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"———-  2020係想點撚樣？？？ ————-","createTime":"2020-06-16T19:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T20:34:56.000Z","uid":13513,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"12bcba08b5db4f9b732c59e18062c68f36c3ad25","tid":2067152,"uid":13513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T19:53:11.000Z","msg":"1月： 美國同伊朗差啲正式開戰<br />\n<br />\n2月：澳洲大火<br />\n<br />\n3月：武肺失控 Global pandemic<br />\n<br />\n4月：全球quarantine 經濟重創 + 美國證實以前有影到UFO<br />\n<br />\n5月：俄羅斯漏2萬噸柴油係北極圈西伯利亞Norilsk安柏那亞河 + 美國種族鬥爭 西方文革現象蒲頭<br />\n<br />\n6月：南北韓局勢嚴重升溫+ 支印邊境互片（btw 印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得之前有人話 解讀「瑪雅預言」方法有誤差<br />\n所以2012先無世界末日 因為2020先係真實日期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而如果佢地今次無解錯 下星期6月21號就係全世界一齊收皮既日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218c4988eb673b5b058953054ed5ad309f23c037","tid":2067152,"uid":215249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T19:55:00.000Z","msg":"幾得意"},{"pid":"840793dc49c59188e370e7855bcf640ba7d4cda6","tid":2067152,"uid":59976,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T19:55:40.000Z","msg":"來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49f38445b6100293eb21a7d7365626a169421db","tid":2067152,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T19:55:51.000Z","msg":"6月21會發生咩事?"},{"pid":"213d2f30048c325ced9956f9c9f079eb1660f1c3","tid":2067152,"uid":306052,"li